genresAdvancedInfo.name: goa trance
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Goa trance is a subgenre of trance music that originated in Goa, India in the 1990s. It is characterized by its use of complex melodies, hypnotic rhythms, and psychedelic sounds. The genre is often associated with spiritual and mystical experiences, and is popular in the festival and rave scenes.
